oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Elmer Todd and Donald in a mule-drawn wagon
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Elmer Todd and baby Donald in a mule-drawn wagon, in Glen Mary. They are on what would later become US Highway 27. There is also an unidentified boy in the wagon.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Roads; Families; Carts & wagons; Mules; Infants
